{
  "texts": [
    "Skilled teachers can guide learners at different levels through complex topics, offering tailored and accessible explanations.",
    "One-on-one tutoring delivered by humans is costly, and skilled teachers are not available everywhere, but GenAI tools may have some of the same benefits at a fraction of the cost.",
    "LLMs show promise as a tool for explaining challenging concepts to graduate medical trainees in a manner tailored to the learner's level (18), and LLMs could be configured to act as personalized tutors (59).",
    "In one study, an LLM successfully reviewed trainee-generated radiology reports and generated relevant (60).",
    "GME trainees preparing for board examinations often use question banks to study, and GME programs use board-exam style questions to assess trainee progress."
  ]
}